snippet.title: LIVE A LIVE - Nintendo Direct Mini: Partner Showcase | 6.28.2022
snippet.description:
LIVE A LIVE comes to Nintendo Switch on July 22, 2022! Download the demo today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/live-a-live-switch/

Seven heroes, seven unique stories. Which one will you play first?

The demo with the beginning of three chapters is available now on Nintendo eShop. Play today and carry your progress over when the game launches!

#LIVEALIVE #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
